column2: SELECT TOP # G.objID, GN.distance, G.u, G.g, G.r, G.i, G.z, a.* FROM Galaxy as G JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#., #, #) AS GN ON G.objID = GN.objID join GalSpecLine as a on G.SpecobjID = a.SpecObjID join stellarMassPCAWiscBC0# AS pca ON G.specobjid = pca.specobjid join emissionLinesPort as emline on pca.specobjid = emline.specobjid JOIN specObj as sp ON emline.specobjid = sp.specobjid
